title: Star Trek Planet of No Return
creator: DEVILS DUE DIGITAL, INC. A Checker Digital Company

extendedInfo.description: Captain's Log, Stardate 18:09.2: It was the strangest civilization in all the known universe - - more awesome than a man could conceive! And the expedition team from the Star Spaceship USS Enterprise soon regretted their decision to explore K-G... Issue 1 - "K-G, The Planet of Death" July 1967 is the first issue ever of the Western Gold Key Imprint.
